title: Jazz Performance - Rene Marie - February 23, 2015
teaser: Jazz vocalist Rene Marie has been a big favorite on WUSF, and throughout the jazz world, for the past few years. And she stops by All Night Jazz for a visit with Bob Seymour. Hear some live music from our studio with Rene Marie.
